        <aside class="about-boxes">
            <section class="info-aside" id="dep-size"><div class="dep-info-aside"><h2 class="small-caps">beck depression inventory</h2>
                <p>This is the Beck Depression Inventory. It is NOT a replacement for seeking medical/professional help. However, this inventory can help you assess the severity of your depression and what symptoms might be causing problems the most. If you feel like you are actively suicidal, please reach out for help. Check for resources on the <a href="selfharm" id="beck" title="self-harm">Self-Harm page.</a> Please choose the answer that cooresponds most closely with how you feel today. There are 21 questions.</p></div></section>
