                      <span class="checkmark"></span>
                    </label>
                    <label class="qbox">I blame myself for everything bad that happens.
                      <input type="radio" name="q8" value=3>
                      <span class="checkmark"></span>
                    </label>

                    <h6 class="small-caps" id="q9">question 9</h6>
                    <label class="qbox">I don't have any thoughts of killing myself.
                      <input type="radio" checked="checked" name="q9" value=0>
